# PURPOSE:
# This file keeps the backups/ folder
# inside Git even when the folder is empty.



# WHY IMPORTANT:
# Git does not keep empty folders.
# .gitkeep prevents the folder from disappearing.



# USED FOR FUTURE:
# - MongoDB backups
# - Database exports
# - Emergency restore files
# - Production snapshots
# - Atlas dump files



# MVP STATUS:
# ✅ SAFE
# ✅ EMPTY
# ✅ NO EXECUTION
# ✅ NO SERVER IMPACT
# ✅ NO PERFORMANCE IMPACT
# ✅ NO CRASH
# ✅ NO IMPORT ERRORS



# IMPORTANT:
# Do NOT store huge backup files in GitHub.
# Add real backups to .gitignore later.



# EXAMPLE FUTURE FILES:
#
# backup-2026-01-01.gz
# mongo-export.json
# atlas-backup.archive
#
# NOT NEEDED NOW.



# FINAL RESULT:
